OL,3,CAlderney has 'lost confidence' in
OL,4,CAurigny, says senior politician
OL,6,FAlderney's senior political committee
OL,7,Fsays the public have "lost confidence"
OL,8,Fin Aurigny amid frustration over
OL,9,Fdelays, cancellations and operational
OL,10,Fissues with its new Twin Otter
OL,11,Faircraft.
OL,13,FIn a scathing attack, Jeannie Cameron,
OL,14,FChair of Alderney's Policy and Finance
OL,15,FCommittee, told ITV News: "We are
OL,16,Fbeing inundated like no other issue
OL,17,Fbefore with (questions about) why is
OL,18,Fthis happening?
OL,26,@yD@MpmyD@]pn
