OL,3,CAlderney has 'lost confidence' in
OL,4,CAurigny, says senior politician
OL,6,F"Aurigny's management are inconsistent
OL,7,Fwith their messaging and we just want
OL,8,Fclarity.
OL,10,F"This is just completely out of order
OL,11,Fand the confidence has gone."
OL,13,FSince retiring its Dornier planes in
OL,14,FNovember, Alderney has been served by
OL,15,Fjust one Twin Otter aircraft for all
OL,16,Fits flights.
OL,18,FKevin Collins was stuck in Southampton
OL,19,Ffor three days and says a lack of
OL,20,Fflights to and from the island is a
OL,21,Fmajor problem.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
