CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1773436318
OL,3,CAlderney has 'lost confidence' in
OL,4,CAurigny, says senior politician
OL,6,FMr Collins said: "There was a bit of
OL,7,Ffog on Sunday morning and if there'd
OL,8,Fbeen a second Twin Otter, it would've
OL,9,Fcleared the backlog very quickly so
OL,10,Fyes, that's the frustration. I know
OL,11,Fother people have said the same on
OL,12,FFacebook - 'it's a clear day, why are
OL,13,Fthere delays?'"
OL,15,FAurigny have admitted that some of the
OL,16,Frecent delays and cancellations were
OL,17,Fcaused by operational issues but add
OL,18,Fthat overall disruption to flights has
OL,19,Fdecreased by 8% since bringing in the
OL,20,FTwin Otter with passenger numbers
OL,21,Fincreasing by 4.3%.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
