OL,3,CAlderney has 'lost confidence' in
OL,4,CAurigny, says senior politician
OL,6,FHowever, calls are growing for
OL,7,Fpoliticians in Guernsey to rethink
OL,8,Fwhether Aurigny should be allowed to
OL,9,Fcontinue operating its lifeline routes.
OL,11,FThe States of Guernsey gave Aurigny a
OL,12,Fsubsidy of #1.5 million in 2025 to
OL,13,Foperate its routes to Alderney and
OL,14,FSouthampton.
OL,16,FHowever, the airline was running at a
OL,17,Flost of #6.5 million, according to the
OL,18,Fcompany's latest published accounts.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
