OL,3,CAlderney has 'lost confidence' in
OL,4,CAurigny, says senior politician
OL,6,FWith this in mind, Joe Mooney, from
OL,7,Fthe Guernsey Aviation Action Group,
OL,8,Ftold ITV News: "We had a reply from
OL,9,Fthe Policy and Resources Committee a
OL,10,Fcouple of months ago saying they went
OL,11,Fout to tender in 2020 and that Aurigny
OL,12,Fwas the most creditable, most viable,
OL,13,Fcost effective and efficient airline
OL,14,Fto run this (lifeline link). That was
OL,15,Fsix years ago.
OL,17,F"This contract needs to go out to
OL,18,Ftender now."
